[6] Shigellosis - USA (IL)
Date: Fri 12 Mar 2010
Source: Chicago Breaking News [edited]
<http://www.chicagobreakingnews.com/2010/03/50-sickened-in-lombard-sandwich-shop-outbreak.html>


The number of people sickened by a shigellosis outbreak traced to a
Lombard sandwich shop is now at 50, DuPage County Health Department
spokesman David Hass said this afternoon, 12 Mar 2010.

Hass added that all 10 people who were hospitalized for the illness
have been discharged. "It's still an ongoing investigation," Hass
said.

The restaurant is closed and a re-opening date has not been set, Hass said.

[Byline: Ted Gregory]

